{"tid":1538862,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[手足情] 4／9 至7／9係休息期，儲怒氣值","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:10.000Z","uid":8948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5253ce6ce27ecb71932a85681e54ea40f2424185","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"八月尾九月頭接連都有唔同活動＋集會<br />\n不論係前線，後勤，文宣，和理非都過左好多晚痛心既無眠夜，<br />\n無數既負面資訊排山倒海咁湧入腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候抖一抖，回一回氣<br />\n保持抗爭力量，休息係好重要既一環<br />\n我建議黎緊每個weekend 都只需要keep住一次大型活動<br />\n其餘飯後活動就因各區而異，但大前提係不被捕，保持抗爭人數<br />\n<br />\n首先用10分鐘照顧一下自己心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F%25E7%2594%25A8-10-%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%25E7%2585%25A7%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%2F444597819473358%2F&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=eb19c0a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/%E7%94%A8-10-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E7%85%A7%E9%A1%A7%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/444597819473358/</a><br />\n<br />\n嘗試擺低所有新聞，做一啲自己好耐冇做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靜靜地飲杯咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇返甩左好耐既劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，去戲院睇返套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同朋友食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，見下女男朋友（如果有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），睇下女優有冇新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等等<br />\n<br />\n然後每晚十點鐘就將所有憤怒化為行動，十點鐘對窗大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qrpi8cy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrpi8cy.jpg&h=97148ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>休息不是遺忘，是為了一起走下去。<br />\n<br />\n香港人！加油！贏就一齊贏，輸就一齊輸，一個都不能少！<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=6257a8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n同意請正評推post"},{"pid":"b14de2914ee134297e6af647d5dedcf24ae68d85","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ad60025553a2dbfaeb466613cfbd84fca86edb1","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76444213cab70b1008dff3c798d5da79494f7b61","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b1bd397e9d363b273a6dd25577f3f54735156f1","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f7a731cbce1f3b6fcc8c4b4810c4b942feb0c50","tid":1538862,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"7/9和你塞"},{"pid":"a858761099e518efac38487cb2dfa470e176af4f","tid":1538862,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"7號機場壓測"},{"pid":"e6c67703481df28561c9055f0e06939da7397c64","tid":1538862,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f7a731cbce1f3b6fcc8c4b4810c4b942feb0c50","tid":1538862,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"7/9和你塞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"sorry，改改佢先"}]}